{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":833,"text":"An 18-year-old, African-American male\njoined the United States Air Force"},{"time":6331,"text":"and was assigned to Mountain Home \nAir Force Base"},{"time":9585,"text":"and was a part of the air police squadron."},{"time":12472,"text":"Upon first arriving there,\nthe first goal that I had"},{"time":16121,"text":"was for me to identify an apartment,"},{"time":18897,"text":"so I could bring my wife \nand my new baby, Melanie,"},{"time":22717,"text":"out to join me in Idaho."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24707,"text":"I immediately went to \nthe personnel office,"},{"time":27219,"text":"and talking with the guys in personnel,"},{"time":29153,"text":"they said, \"Hey, no problem finding \nan apartment in Mountain Home, Idaho."},{"time":34319,"text":"The people down there love us \nbecause they know if they have an airman"},{"time":39509,"text":"who is coming in to rent \none of their apartments,"},{"time":41872,"text":"they'll always get their money.\""},{"time":44235,"text":"And that was a really important thing."},{"time":46108,"text":"He said, \"So here is a list \nof people that you can call,"},{"time":48927,"text":"and then they will then allow you \nto select the apartment that you want.\""},{"time":52942,"text":"So I got the list; I made the call."},{"time":55806,"text":"The lady answered on the other end\nand I told her what I wanted."},{"time":58824,"text":"She said, \"Oh, great you called."},{"time":61126,"text":"We have four or five apartments\navailable right now.\""},{"time":65078,"text":"She said, \"Do you want \na one-bedroom or two-bedroom?\""},{"time":68072,"text":"Then she said, \"Let's not talk about that.\n"},{"time":70125,"text":"Just come on down, \nselect the apartment that you want."},{"time":72946,"text":"We'll sign the contract"},{"time":74834,"text":"and you'll have keys in your hand\nto get your family out here right away.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":78741,"text":"So I was excited."},{"time":80270,"text":"I jumped in my car. I went downtown\nand knocked on the door."},{"time":83666,"text":"When I knocked on the door, \nthe woman came to the door,"},{"time":86327,"text":"and she looked at me, and she said,\n\"Can I help you?\""},{"time":89261,"text":"I said, \"Yes, I'm the person \nwho called about the apartments."},{"time":93102,"text":"I was just coming down \nto make my selection.\""},{"time":95516,"text":"She said, \"You know what? \nI'm really sorry,"},{"time":98052,"text":"but my husband rented those apartments\nand didn't tell me about them.\""},{"time":102140,"text":"I said, \"You mean he rented \nall five of them in one hour?\""},{"time":107075,"text":"She didn't give me a response,\nand what she said was this:"},{"time":110460,"text":"She said, \"Why don't you\nleave your number,"},{"time":112685,"text":"and if we have some openings, \nI'll give you a call?\""},{"time":115722,"text":"Needless to say,\nI did not get a call from her."},{"time":119004,"text":"Nor did I get any responses \nfrom the other people"},{"time":122280,"text":"that they gave me on the list\nwhere I could get apartments."}]},{"cues":[{"time":125801,"text":"So as a result of that,\nand feeling rejected,"},{"time":128092,"text":"I went back to the base, and I talked\nto the squadron commander."},{"time":131978,"text":"His name was McDow, Major McDow."},{"time":134244,"text":"I said, \"Major McDow, I need your help.\""},{"time":136436,"text":"I told him what happened, \nand here's what he said to me:"},{"time":139111,"text":"He said, \"James, I would love to help you."},{"time":141453,"text":"But you know the problem:"},{"time":143182,"text":"We can't make people rent to folks \nthat they don't want to rent to."},{"time":147416,"text":"And besides, we have a great relationship\nwith people in the community"},{"time":151914,"text":"and we really don't want to damage that.\""},{"time":153956,"text":"He said, \"So maybe this is \nwhat you should do."},{"time":156226,"text":"Why don't you let your family stay home,"},{"time":158864,"text":"because you do know \nthat you get a 30-day leave."},{"time":161818,"text":"So once a year,"},{"time":163213,"text":"you can go home to your family,\nspend 30 days and then come on back.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":167818,"text":"Needless to say, that didn't\nresonate for me."},{"time":169988,"text":"So after leaving him, \nI went back to personnel,"},{"time":172914,"text":"and talking to the clerk,"},{"time":174414,"text":"he said, \"Jim, I think I have a \nsolution for you."},{"time":177215,"text":"There's an airman who is leaving\nand he has a trailer."},{"time":181507,"text":"If you noticed, in Mountain Home,"},{"time":183343,"text":"there are trailer parks and trailers\nall over the place."},{"time":185991,"text":"You can buy his trailer,\nand you'd probably get a really good deal"},{"time":189534,"text":"because he wants to get out of town\nas soon as possible."},{"time":192208,"text":"And that would take care of your problem,"},{"time":194190,"text":"and that would provide \nthe solution for you.\""},{"time":196342,"text":"So I immediately jumped in my car,\nwent downtown, saw the trailer --"},{"time":199578,"text":"it was a small trailer,"},{"time":201422,"text":"but under the circumstances,"},{"time":203032,"text":"I figured that was the \nbest thing that I could do."},{"time":205447,"text":"So I bought the trailer."},{"time":207008,"text":"And then I asked him, \n\"Can I just leave the trailer here,"},{"time":210279,"text":"and that would take care \nof all my problems,"},{"time":212513,"text":"I wouldn't have to find\nanother trailer park?\""},{"time":214682,"text":"He said, \"Before I say yes to that, \nI need to check with management.\""},{"time":218536,"text":"So I get back to the base,"},{"time":219968,"text":"he called me back and management said,"},{"time":222125,"text":"\"No, you can't leave the trailer here"},{"time":224569,"text":"because we had promised that slot\nto some other people.\""},{"time":228133,"text":"And that was strange to me"},{"time":229944,"text":"because there were several \nother slots that were open,"},{"time":232515,"text":"but it just so happened that he \nhad promised that slot to someone else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236202,"text":"So, what I did --"},{"time":237504,"text":"and he said, \"You shouldn't worry, Jim,\nbecause there are a lot of trailer parks.\""},{"time":241571,"text":"So I put out another exhaustive list\nof going to trailer parks."},{"time":245420,"text":"I went to one after another, \nafter another."},{"time":247490,"text":"And I got the same kind of rejection there"},{"time":250092,"text":"that I received when I was looking \nfor the apartment."},{"time":254221,"text":"And as a result, the kind of comments\nthat they made to me,"},{"time":258550,"text":"in addition to saying that they\ndidn't have any slots open,"},{"time":262753,"text":"one person said, \"Jim, the reason\nwhy we can't rent to you,"},{"time":267008,"text":"we already have a Negro family\nin the trailer park.\""},{"time":271188,"text":"He said, \"And it's not me, \nbecause I like you people.\""},{"time":275224,"text":"(Laughs)"},{"time":276526,"text":"And that's what I did, too.\nI chuckled, too."},{"time":280257,"text":"He said, \"But here's the problem:"},{"time":282233,"text":"If I let you in, the other tenants \nwill move out"},{"time":286542,"text":"and I can't afford to take\nthat kind of a hit.\""},{"time":289725,"text":"He said, \"I just can't rent to you.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":292052,"text":"Even though that was discouraging,\nit didn't stop me."},{"time":294603,"text":"I kept looking,"},{"time":295933,"text":"and I looked at the far end \nof the town in Mountain Home,"},{"time":300233,"text":"and there was a small trailer park."},{"time":302327,"text":"I mean, a really small trailer park."},{"time":304414,"text":"It didn't have any paved roads in it,"},{"time":306462,"text":"it didn't have the concrete slabs,"},{"time":308470,"text":"it didn't have fencing"},{"time":310019,"text":"to portion off your trailer slot \nfrom other trailer slots."},{"time":313111,"text":"It didn't have a laundry facility."},{"time":314923,"text":"But the conclusion I reached \nat that moment"},{"time":317116,"text":"was that I didn't have \na lot of other options."},{"time":319398,"text":"So I called my wife, and I said,\n\"We're going to make this one work.\""},{"time":322854,"text":"And we moved into it"},{"time":324399,"text":"and we became homeowners\nin Mountain Home, Idaho."},{"time":328117,"text":"And of course, eventually\nthings settled down."}]},{"cues":[{"time":332758,"text":"Four years after that, I received papers\nto move from Mountain Home, Idaho"},{"time":338236,"text":"to a place called Goose Bay, Labrador."},{"time":341270,"text":"We won't even talk about that.\nIt was another great location. (Laughter)"},{"time":345180,"text":"So my challenge then was to get my family \nfrom Mountain Home, Idaho"},{"time":349888,"text":"to Sharon, Pennsylvania."},{"time":351639,"text":"That wasn't a problem because we\nhad just purchased a brand-new automobile."},{"time":355169,"text":"My mother called \nand said she'll fly out."},{"time":357569,"text":"She'll be with us as we drive,\nshe'll help us manage the children."},{"time":361951,"text":"So she came out, her and Alice \nput a lot of food together for the trip."}]},{"cues":[{"time":365881,"text":"That morning, we left at about 5 a.m."},{"time":368964,"text":"Great trip, having a great time, \ngood conversation."},{"time":372110,"text":"Somewhere around 6:30, 7 o'clock,\nwe got a little bit tired,"},{"time":375944,"text":"and we said, \"Why don't we get\na motel so that we can rest"},{"time":378783,"text":"and then have an early start\nin the morning?\""},{"time":381164,"text":"So we were looking at a number \nof the motels as we drove down the road,"},{"time":384544,"text":"and we saw one, it was a great\nbig, bright flashing light that said,"},{"time":388021,"text":"\"Vacancies, Vacancies, Vacanies.\""},{"time":390325,"text":"So we stopped in."},{"time":391622,"text":"They were in the parking lot, \nI went inside."},{"time":393807,"text":"When I walked inside,"},{"time":395134,"text":"the lady was just finishing up \none contract with some folks,"},{"time":398311,"text":"some other people \nwere coming in behind me."},{"time":400400,"text":"And so I walked to the counter,"},{"time":402133,"text":"and she said, \"How can I help you?\""},{"time":404296,"text":"I said, \"I would like to get a motel \nfor the evening for my family.\""},{"time":407556,"text":"She said, \"You know, I'm really sorry,\nI just rented the last one."},{"time":412058,"text":"We will not have any more \nuntil the morning.\""},{"time":414704,"text":"She said, \"But if you go down the road\nabout an hour, 45 minutes,"},{"time":418685,"text":"there's another trailer park down there.\""},{"time":421030,"text":"I said, \"Yeah, but you still have the \n'Vacancies' light on, and it's flashing.\""},{"time":424811,"text":"She said, \"Oh, I forgot.\""},{"time":426287,"text":"And she reached over \nand turned the light off."},{"time":428663,"text":"She looked at me and I looked at her."},{"time":430904,"text":"There were other people in the room."},{"time":432662,"text":"She kind of looked at them.\nNo one said anything."},{"time":435068,"text":"So I just got the hint and I left,\nand went outside to the parking lot."},{"time":438424,"text":"And I told my mother and I told my wife\nand also Melanie, and I said,"},{"time":442574,"text":"\"It looks like we're going to have to\ndrive a little bit further down the road"},{"time":446370,"text":"to be able to sleep tonight.\""},{"time":448726,"text":"And we did drive down the road,"},{"time":450899,"text":"but just before we took off \nand pulled out of the parking lot,"},{"time":454421,"text":"guess what happened?"},{"time":455914,"text":"The light came back on."},{"time":457733,"text":"And it said, \"Vacancies, \nVacancies, Vacancies.\""},{"time":460593,"text":"We were able to find a nice place."},{"time":462979,"text":"It wasn't our preference,\nbut it was secure and it was clean."},{"time":467715,"text":"And so we had a great sleep that night."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470537,"text":"The piece that's important about that"},{"time":472356,"text":"is that we had similar\nkinds of experiences"},{"time":475468,"text":"from Idaho all the way through \nto Pennsylvania,"},{"time":478650,"text":"where we were rejected from hotels, \nmotels and restaurants."},{"time":482951,"text":"But we made it to Pennsylvania."},{"time":485151,"text":"We got the family settled.\nEveryone was glad to see the kids."},{"time":489711,"text":"I jumped on a plane and shot off\nto Goose Bay, Labrador,"},{"time":494286,"text":"which is another story, right?"},{"time":495947,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":498234,"text":"Here it is, 53 years later,"},{"time":502657,"text":"I now have nine grandchildren, \ntwo great-grandchildren."},{"time":507086,"text":"Five of the grandchildren are boys."},{"time":509863,"text":"I have master's, Ph.D., undergrad,\none in medical school."},{"time":515076,"text":"I have a couple that are trending."},{"time":517690,"text":"They're almost there but not quite.\n(Laughter)"},{"time":520455,"text":"I have one who has been \nin college now for eight years."},{"time":523555,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":524975,"text":"He doesn't have a degree yet, \nbut he wants to be a comedian."},{"time":528346,"text":"So we're just trying to get him\nto stay in school."},{"time":531464,"text":"Because you never know,"},{"time":532994,"text":"just because you're funny at home,\ndoes not make you a comedian, right?"},{"time":536894,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":538646,"text":"But the thing about it, \nthey're all good kids --"},{"time":541078,"text":"no drugs, no babies \nin high school, no crime."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545338,"text":"So with that being the backdrop,"},{"time":547896,"text":"I was sitting in my TV room watching TV,"},{"time":550117,"text":"and they were talking about Ferguson\nand all the hullabaloo that was going on."},{"time":554670,"text":"And all of a sudden, one of the news \ncommentators got on the air and she said,"},{"time":560141,"text":"\"In the last three months,"},{"time":562939,"text":"eight unarmed African-American males"},{"time":566808,"text":"have been killed by police,\nwhite homeowners, or white citizens.\""},{"time":574777,"text":"For some reason, at that moment\nit just all hit me."},{"time":577495,"text":"I said, \"What is it? It is so insane."},{"time":581487,"text":"What is the hatred that's causing people \nto do these kinds of things?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":586625,"text":"Just then, one of my grandsons called."},{"time":589073,"text":"He said, \"Granddad, did you hear\nwhat they said on TV?\""},{"time":592312,"text":"I said, \"Yes, I did.\""},{"time":593770,"text":"He said, \"I'm just so confused."},{"time":595524,"text":"We do everything we do,\nbut it seems that driving while black,"},{"time":600094,"text":"walking while black, talking while black,\nit's just dangerous."},{"time":604494,"text":"What can we do? We do everything\nthat you told us to do."},{"time":609373,"text":"When stopped by the police,"},{"time":611163,"text":"we place both hands on the steering wheel\nat the 12 o'clock position."},{"time":615140,"text":"If asked to get identification,"},{"time":617767,"text":"we tell them, 'I am slowly reaching over \ninto the glove compartment to get my I.D.'"},{"time":623675,"text":"When pulled out of the car to be searched,"},{"time":626440,"text":"when laid on the ground to be searched,"},{"time":628589,"text":"when our trunks are opened to be searched,"},{"time":630731,"text":"we don't push back, we don't challenge\nbecause we know, you've told us,"},{"time":634991,"text":"'Don't you challenge the police."},{"time":637030,"text":"After it's over, call us and we'll\nbe the ones to challenge.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":640638,"text":"He said, \"And this is the piece \nthat really bugs me:"},{"time":643370,"text":"Our white friends, our buddies,\nwe kind of hang together."},{"time":646988,"text":"When they hear about these kinds\nof things happening to us, they say,"},{"time":650225,"text":"'Why do you take it?"},{"time":652413,"text":"You need to push back.\nYou need to challenge."},{"time":655392,"text":"You need to ask them \nfor their identification.'\""},{"time":658154,"text":"And here's what the boys have been\ntaught to tell them:"},{"time":660761,"text":"\"We know that you can do that,\nbut please do not do that"},{"time":663987,"text":"while we're in the car"},{"time":666026,"text":"because the consequences for you\nare significantly different"},{"time":669813,"text":"than the consequences for us.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":671862,"text":"And so as a grandparent, \nwhat do I tell my grandsons?"},{"time":675360,"text":"How do I keep them safe?\nHow do I keep them alive?"},{"time":678706,"text":"As a result of this, people have\ncome to me and said, \n"},{"time":681227,"text":"\"Jim, are you angry?\""},{"time":685498,"text":"And my response to that is this:"},{"time":688619,"text":"\"I don't have the luxury of being angry,"},{"time":694065,"text":"and I also know the consequences \nof being enraged.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":699075,"text":"So therefore, the only thing that I can do"},{"time":701168,"text":"is take my collective intellect and my\nenergy and my ideas and my experiences"},{"time":707456,"text":"and dedicate myself to challenge, \nat any point in time,"},{"time":711445,"text":"anything that looks \nlike it might be racist."},{"time":714326,"text":"So the first thing I have \nto do is to educate,"},{"time":717059,"text":"the second thing I have to do \nis to unveil racism,"},{"time":720327,"text":"and the last thing I need to do\nis do everything within my power"},{"time":723727,"text":"to eradicate racism in my lifetime\nby any means necessary."}]},{"cues":[{"time":730864,"text":"The second thing I do is this:"},{"time":733290,"text":"I want to appeal to Americans."},{"time":736976,"text":"I want to appeal to their humanity,\nto their dignity,"},{"time":741420,"text":"to their civic pride and ownership"},{"time":745887,"text":"to be able to not react to these \nheinous crimes in an adverse manner."},{"time":753952,"text":"But instead, to elevate your level\nof societal knowledge,"},{"time":760061,"text":"your level of societal awareness\nand societal consciousness"},{"time":764465,"text":"to then collectively come together,\nall of us come together,"},{"time":768484,"text":"to make sure that we speak out against\nand we challenge any kind of insanity,"},{"time":775552,"text":"any kind of insanity that makes it \nokay to kill unarmed people,"},{"time":782753,"text":"regardless of their ethnicity,\n"},{"time":785335,"text":"regardless of their race,"},{"time":787438,"text":"regardless of their diversity makeup."}]},{"cues":[{"time":789925,"text":"We have to challenge that.\nIt doesn't make any sense."},{"time":793185,"text":"The only way I think we can do that\nis through a collective."},{"time":797014,"text":"We need to have black and white \nand Asian and Hispanic"},{"time":800914,"text":"just to step forward and say,"},{"time":802614,"text":"\"We are not going to accept \nthat kind of behavior anymore.\""}]}]}